quran[47]{c,v,t}:
  72,1,"“Nena (iwe Mtumiki (s.a.w), kwa anthu ako): “Kwavumbulutsidwa kwa ine kuti gulu la ziwanda lidamvetsera (kuwerenga kwanga kwa Qur’an) ndipo lidanena (kumtundu wawo): ndithu tamvetsera Qur’an yodabwitsa (ikuwerengedwa)"
  72,2,"“Ikuitanira kuchilungamo, ndipo taikhulupirira. Ndipo sitimphatikiza aliyense ndi Mbuye wathu, (pa mapemphero)"
  72,3,“Ndipo ndithu ukulu ndi ulemelero wa Mbuye wathu watukuka; sadadzipangire mkazi kapena mwana
  72,4,“Ndipo ndithu mbuli za mwa ife zakhala zikunenera Allah mawu abodza (okhala kutali ndi choonadi)
  72,5,“Ndipo ndithu ife tinkaganiza kuti anthu ndi ziwanda sangamnenere Allah zabodza (zosayenera ulemelero Wake)
  72,6,"“Ndipo ndithu padali amuna a mu wanthu amapempha chitetezo kwa amuna amziwanda, ndipo adawaonjezera (amuna amziwanda) kupitiriza machimo (awo, kupulikira ndi kuchenjelera anthu)"
  72,7,“Ndipo ndithu iwo amaganiza monga momwe mumaganizira inu kuti Allah sadzaukitsa aliyense
  72,8,“Ndithu ife tidafuna kukafika kumwamba; tidakupeza kutadzala alonda (angelo) amphamvu ndi zenje za moto
  72,9,“Ndithu ife tidali kukhala m’menemo (kale) mokhala momvetsera; (mobera nkhani zakumwamba). Koma amene afune kumvetsera tsopano apeza chenje cha moto chikudikilira (kuti chimgwere iye ndi kumuononga)
  72,10,"“Ndithu ife sitikudziwa chilango chimene akuwafunira a m’dziko (polondera kumwamba, kuletsa kumvetsera nkhani zakumeneko); kapena Mbuye wawo akuwafunira zabwino ndi chilungamo (pa zimenezo)"
  72,11,“Ndithu ena mwa ife ndi abwino koma ena sali choncho. Tili njira zosiyanasiyana
  72,12,"“Ndithu ife tidadziwa kuti Allah sitingathe kumlepheretsa (lamulo Lake pa ife paliponse tingakhale) pa dziko lapansi, ndipo sitingamlepheretsenso pomzemba ndi kuthawira (kumwamba)"
  72,13,“Ndipo ife pamene tachimva chiongoko (Qur’an) tachikhulupirira ndipo amene ati akhulupirire mwa Mbuye wake saopa kumchepetsera (chabwino kapena kumuonjezera machimo ake)
  72,14,"“Ndithu mwa ife alipo Asilamu ndiponso mwa ife alipo opatuka (mu njira ya chilungamo); amene walowa m’Chisilamu, iwowo ndi amene alunjika njira ya choonadi"
  72,15,“Koma opatuka (kunjira ya chilungamo) adzakhala nkhuni za Jahannam.”
  72,16,“Ndithu (anthu ndi ziwanda) akadalungama panjira ya chilungamo tikadawamwetsa madzi ambiri (okwanira nyengo zonse)
  72,17,"“Kuti tiwayese ndi zimenezo (mmene angamyamikire Allah pa mtendere Wake pa iwo). Koma amene anyozera kupembedza Mbuye wake, amlowetsa ku chilango chovuta (chimene sangathe kupirira nacho)"
  72,18,"“Ndithu misikiti ndi ya Allah yekha! Choncho, musapembedze aliyense pamodzi ndi Allah"
  72,19,"“Ndipo ndithu pamene adaima kapolo wa Allah (Muhammad{s.a.w}, pa Swala yake) uku akumpembedza (Allah), ziwanda zidatsala pang’ono kumgwera (chifukwa cha kuchuluka kwawo ndi kumzinga podabwa ndi zimene adaziona ndi kuzimva)"
  72,20,"“Nena: “Ndikumpembedza Mbuye wanga M’modzi (Yekha) ndipo sindingamphatikize ndi aliyense (m’mapemphero Ake).”"
  72,21,"“Nena: “Ine ndilibe udindo wokupatsani mavuto kapena chilungamo (ndi zabwino).”"
  72,22,"“Nena: “Ine palibe anganditeteze ku chilango cha Allah (ngati nditamnyoza) sindingapeze malo (othawira kuchilango Chake) kupatula kwa Iye.”"
  72,23,"““Koma (mphamvu imene ndili nayo) ndikufikitsa uthenga wa Allah umene adanditumizira; ndithu amene anyoza Allah ndi Mtumiki Wake (ndi kupatuka pa chipembedzo cha (Allah) ndithu moto wa Jahannam ndi wake, akakhala m’menemo muyaya.”"
  72,24,"“Mpaka pomwe adzaziona zimene alonjezedwa ndipamene adzadziwa (kuti) kodi ndani mwini mthandizi wofooka ndiponso wochepekedwa mchiwerengero (cha omtsatira, iwo kapena Asilamu).”"
  72,25,"“Nena (kuti): “Sindikudziwa ngati zomwe mukulonjezedwa (za chilango) zili pafupi, kapena Mbuye wanga azitalikitsa.”"
  72,26,"““(Iye) ndi wodziwa zobisika; sazionetsa zobisika Zake kwa aliyense (mzolengedwa Zake),”"
  72,27,““Kupatula Mtumiki (Wake) amene wamuyanja; (iyeyo amamdziwitsa zobisikazo) ndipo ndithu amamuikira alonda kutsogolo kwake ndi kumbuyo kwake (omulonda).”
  72,28,"““Kuti adziwe ngati afikitsa uthenga wa Mbuye wawo, ndipo wawazungulira (podziwa zonse zili kwa iwo) ndipo wadziwa kuchuluka kwa zinthu zonse zimene zilipo; (palibe chobisika kwa Iye).”"
  73,1,“E iwe wadzifunditsa (ndi nsalu)
  73,2,"“Imilira usiku (upemphere), kupatula nthawi yochepa"
  73,3,“Theka lake kapena chepetsa thekalo pang’ono (mpaka ufike chimodzi mwa zigawo zitatu za usiku)
  73,4,“Kapena wonjezapo (mpaka ufike zigawo ziwiri mwa zigawo zitatu za usiku;) ndipo werenga Qur’an mofatsa (lemba ndi lemba)
  73,5,“Ife tikuvumbulutsira iwe (Mneneri) mawu olemera (yomwe ndi Qur’an)
  73,6,"“Ndithu kudzuka usiku ndi kuchita mapemphero kumalowelera (mu mtima) kwambiri, ndipo zoyankhula zake zimakhala zoongoka ndi zolunjika bwino (kuposa mapemphero amasana)"
  73,7,“Ndithu masana uli ndi zochitachita zambiri; (umatanganidwa ndi ntchito yauthenga; dzipatse danga usiku polimbika kupemphera)
  73,8,"“Ndipo tchula dzina la Mbuye wako (Amene adalenga ndi kulera zinthu), ndipo udzipereke kwathunthu kwa Iye"
  73,9,“(Iye ndiye) Mbuye wa kuvuma ndi kuzambwe; palibe wopembedzedwa mwachoonadi koma Iye. Mchiteni kukhala Mtetezi (wanu pa zinthu zanu zonse)
  73,10,“Ndipo pirira pa zimene akunena. Ndipo apewe (ndi mtima wako); kupewa kwabwino
  73,11,“Ndisiye Ine ndi otsutsa eni kupeza bwino; ndipo alekelere kanthawi kochepa
  73,12,"“Ndithudi, tili ndi mitundumitundu ya unyolo ndi Moto woyaka"
  73,13,“Ndi chakudya chotsamwitsa ndi chilango chowawa
  73,14,“Tsiku limene nthaka ndi mapiri zidzagwedezeka; (kugwedezeka kwa mphamvu kotero kuti) mapiri adzakhala ngati mulu wa mchenga woyoyoka
  73,15,“Ndithu Ife takutumizirani Mthenga amene adzakhala mboni yanu (tsiku la chimaliziro; monga momwe tidamtumizira (Mûsa) kukhala Mtumiki kwa Firiauni
  73,16,“Koma Firiauni adamnyoza Mtumikiyo; ndipo tidamulanga chilango chokhwima
  73,17,“Kodi mungadzitchinjirize chotani ngati mukana (chilango cha) tsiku (lomwe) lidzachititsa ana kukhala ndi imvi
  73,18,"“Thambo (pamodzi ndi mphamvu zake ndi kukula kwake), lidzang’ambika (tsiku limenelo) chifukwa cha kuopsa kwa tsikulo, lonjezo la (Allah) lidzakwaniritsidwa (palibe wolipinga)"
  73,19,"“Ndithudi, ma Ayah awa (amene akunena za kuwopsa kwa Qiyâma) ndichikumbutso. Choncho amene akufuna (kuthandizika nawo) ayende panjira ya Mbuye wake (pokwaniritsa malamulo Ake ndi kuleka zoipa)"